The following is a list of awards and nominations received by English actor Tom Hardy .
He was nominated for the Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor for the 2015 film The Revenant .
He also won the 2011 BAFTA Rising Star Award , and has twice won the British Independent Film Award for Best Actor , for Bronson ( 2009 ) and Legend ( 2015 ) .
